# vn.py框架的CTP底层接口

<p align="center">
  <img src ="https://vnpy.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/vnpy-logo.png"/>
</p>

<p align="center">
    <img src ="https://img.shields.io/badge/version-6.5.1.8-blueviolet.svg"/>
